{"tid":2432682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：國安處近日又聯絡壹傳媒多名現任和前任管理層 包括20年前已經離職同事","createTime":"2021-03-04T13:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T18:59:24.000Z","uid":22556,"like":30,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8ad912ee01731e1ca677ebb66b55b4a6fac2a7","tid":2432682,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"警隊針對壹傳媒廠房用地的案件再有動作。《蘋果》獲悉，繼日前拘捕壹傳媒前營運總裁丁家裕後，警隊國安處近日又聯絡壹傳媒多名現任和前任管理層，邀請他們到警署「落口供」，包括現任非執行主席葉一堅，以及20年前已經離開壹傳媒的羅燦及何國輝。此外，壹傳媒去年遭警方搜查的多個部門，部份員工亦接獲通知要求「落口供」。《蘋果》已就事件向警方查詢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/F4HDYRT52ZGMROGVM7K2LITY2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2FF4HDYRT52ZGMROGVM7K2LITY2Y%2F&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv%2BSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=08c01a9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2FF4HDYRT52ZGMROGVM7K2LITY2Y%2F&h=ba832838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/F4HDYRT52ZGMROGVM7K2LITY2Y/</a>"},{"pid":"b7b0019f5734f4d0c046402011768bf6fdc6df03","tid":2432682,"uid":226231,"like":12,"dislike":223,"score":-211,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:13:39.000Z","msg":"落口供啫"},{"pid":"98c49131ae27d90d016f4714d2e8a6e80a3e5137","tid":2432682,"uid":47614,"like":107,"dislike":2,"score":105,"quote":{"pid":"b7b0019f5734f4d0c046402011768bf6fdc6df03","tid":2432682,"uid":226231,"like":12,"dislike":223,"score":-211,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:13:39.000Z","msg":"落口供啫"},"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:14:31.000Z","msg":"點解啲五毛狗可以次次做第一個回覆？"},{"pid":"452c6ed03c0de1f921f17bccac7c60b6adea92d1","tid":2432682,"uid":39855,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:15:02.000Z","msg":"估計肥佬黎要坐終身！"},{"pid":"d2d05160b2a04a1882a2e017409de7b2eafc5958","tid":2432682,"uid":19528,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"98c49131ae27d90d016f4714d2e8a6e80a3e5137","tid":243268